Reasoning: The paper discusses the decoding of 5G NR control channel communications using CA-Polar codes, which are related to information theory and communication systems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also discusses the computational efficiency of the decoding algorithm, which could fall under cs.COMM (Networking and Internet Architecture) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Additionally, the paper discusses the performance of the decoding algorithm through simulations, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) or cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
